      <hedline>
        <hl1>It's Time to Talk About Global Warming</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Allan R Shickman letter says global warming is becoming great issue of 21st century (Sept 28 editorial)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>The prophecy is coming true. Global warming is emerging as the great issue of the 21st century.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>The prophecy is coming true. Global warming is emerging as the great issue of the 21st century.</p>
        <p>All of the politically motivated denial cannot stand up to the winds of Katrina. This is an issue that will not go away. Politicians may belittle the scientists, but they cannot belittle the destruction of New Orleans.</p>
        <p>Allan R. Shickman  St. Louis, Sept. 28, 2005</p>
      </block>
